enefits from this wealth and influence, which allows him to engage in various activities, both strategic and morally questionable. [Data: Entities (407, 411), Relationships (699, 704)]\n\n## The Imperial Guard's crucial role in security\n\nThe Imperial Guard (禁军) is a vital military organization responsible for protecting the sovereign, guarding the Eastern Palace, and executing key military tasks. Members of the Imperial Guard, such as 姬野 and 幽隐, play essential roles in maintaining security and order. However, the organization has faced internal discipline issues, including large-scale conflicts and the dismissal of commanders. Despite these challenges, the Imperial Guard remains indispensable for the protection of the state and the royal family. [Data: Entities (168), Relationships (787, 790, 793)]\n\n## 方起召's complex character and influence\n\n方起召 is a multifaceted character with a complex background. As a member of the wealthy Fang family, he enjoys significant social and economic privileges. He is involved in strategic discussions and military tactics but also engages in morally questionable activities, such as bullying and bribery. His interactions with other characters, such as 羽然 and 幽隐, further highlight his complex personality and the social dynamics within the community. [Data: Entities (407), Relationships (699, 702, 703, 704)]\n\n## The cultural significance of the 蛮族人\n\nThe 蛮族人 are a group known for their expertise in wrestling and traditional combat techniques. They are associated with individuals like 吕归尘 and the 黑瞳男孩, who demonstrate wrestling skills characteristic of the 蛮族人. This cultural group adds a layer of diversity and tradition to the community, influencing the social and martial practices within the region. [Data: Entities (457), Relationships (792, 794)]\n\n## The role of 东宫军营 in training and conflicts\n\nThe 东宫军营 serves as a training ground for young warriors, including 姬野 and other members of the Imperial Guard. It is a central location